{"id": "waarom-de-winkelstraat-zichzelf-opnieuw-moet-uitvinden__c4-paragraph__0002", "text": "[Henk Hofstede](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/authors/henk-hofstede/index.html)", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "waarom-de-winkelstraat-zichzelf-opnieuw-moet-uitvinden__c4-paragraph__0002", "source_slug": "waarom-de-winkelstraat-zichzelf-opnieuw-moet-uitvinden", "source_title": "Why the shopping street must reinvent itself", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/retail/waarom-de-winkelstraat-zichzelf-opnieuw-moet-uitvinden.html", "source_date": "2025-09-08", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "retail", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 2, "n_chunks_total": 13, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "waarom-de-winkelstraat-zichzelf-opnieuw-moet-uitvinden__c4-paragraph__0003", "text": "Can the Dutch shopping street still be saved? How can small retailers compete with international chains? Which formulas work and don't? In this first episode of the podcast Achter de Cijfers, journalist Esther van Rijswijk talks to sector banker Henk Hofstede about the shopping street of the future, where it is no longer just about buying things.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "waarom-de-winkelstraat-zichzelf-opnieuw-moet-uitvinden__c4-paragraph__0003", "source_slug": "waarom-de-winkelstraat-zichzelf-opnieuw-moet-uitvinden", "source_title": "Why the shopping street must reinvent itself", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/retail/waarom-de-winkelstraat-zichzelf-opnieuw-moet-uitvinden.html", "source_date": "2025-09-08", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "retail", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 3, "n_chunks_total": 13, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "waarom-de-winkelstraat-zichzelf-opnieuw-moet-uitvinden__c4-paragraph__0004", "text": "Also read the publication [Balancing between spending and saving](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/retail/balanceren- Tussen-spenderen-en-besparen.html) about the hybrid consumer today. A hybrid consumer easily switches between discount and more luxurious purchases. Sometimes he specifically searches for the lowest price and then he goes for A-brands and more luxurious products. It makes the consumer more inconsistent and difficult for retailers to grasp.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "waarom-de-winkelstraat-zichzelf-opnieuw-moet-uitvinden__c4-paragraph__0004", "source_slug": "waarom-de-winkelstraat-zichzelf-opnieuw-moet-uitvinden", "source_title": "Why the shopping street must reinvent itself", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/retail/waarom-de-winkelstraat-zichzelf-opnieuw-moet-uitvinden.html", "source_date": "2025-09-08", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "retail", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 4, "n_chunks_total": 13, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "waarom-de-winkelstraat-zichzelf-opnieuw-moet-uitvinden__c4-paragraph__0005", "text": "Curious about what's going on behind the biggest economic developments? In the podcast [Achter de Cijfers](https://www.abnamro.com/nl/podcast-achter-de-figures) we take you through a current topic every week, together with experts. From unaffordable housing to rising inflation, we explain it clearly and without jargon. Because economics is more than figures and graphs, it's about your wallet. Behind the Numbers is the economics teacher you always wanted.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "waarom-de-winkelstraat-zichzelf-opnieuw-moet-uitvinden__c4-paragraph__0005", "source_slug": "waarom-de-winkelstraat-zichzelf-opnieuw-moet-uitvinden", "source_title": "Why the shopping street must reinvent itself", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/retail/waarom-de-winkelstraat-zichzelf-opnieuw-moet-uitvinden.html", "source_date": "2025-09-08", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "retail", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 5, "n_chunks_total": 13, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "waarom-de-winkelstraat-zichzelf-opnieuw-moet-uitvinden__c4-paragraph__0006", "text": "Our experts and representatives will discuss current topics with entrepreneurs and others on various stages and platforms. They talk about matters such as sustainable entrepreneurship, circular economy, real estate and social impact. Follow the webinars, podcasts and interviews.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "waarom-de-winkelstraat-zichzelf-opnieuw-moet-uitvinden__c4-paragraph__0006", "source_slug": "waarom-de-winkelstraat-zichzelf-opnieuw-moet-uitvinden", "source_title": "Why the shopping street must reinvent itself", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/retail/waarom-de-winkelstraat-zichzelf-opnieuw-moet-uitvinden.html", "source_date": "2025-09-08", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "retail", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 6, "n_chunks_total": 13, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "waarom-de-winkelstraat-zichzelf-opnieuw-moet-uitvinden__c4-paragraph__0007", "text": "[Watch the videos or listen to the podcasts](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/in-spraak/index.html)", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "waarom-de-winkelstraat-zichzelf-opnieuw-moet-uitvinden__c4-paragraph__0007", "source_slug": "waarom-de-winkelstraat-zichzelf-opnieuw-moet-uitvinden", "source_title": "Why the shopping street must reinvent itself", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/retail/waarom-de-winkelstraat-zichzelf-opnieuw-moet-uitvinden.html", "source_date": "2025-09-08", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "retail", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 7, "n_chunks_total": 13, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "waarom-de-winkelstraat-zichzelf-opnieuw-moet-uitvinden__c4-paragraph__0008", "text": "Today's store is more than just a pantry. It offers customers advice and inspiration and is the place to be in contact with customers. Due to the Ukraine crisis and significant inflation, consumer confidence has fallen sharply and this affects consumer behavior. Retailers are also faced with significant cost increases in the areas of purchasing, rent, personnel costs, Covid recovery payments and energy. Circumstances remain challenging for many retailers even after Covid.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "waarom-de-winkelstraat-zichzelf-opnieuw-moet-uitvinden__c4-paragraph__0008", "source_slug": "waarom-de-winkelstraat-zichzelf-opnieuw-moet-uitvinden", "source_title": "Why the shopping street must reinvent itself", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/retail/waarom-de-winkelstraat-zichzelf-opnieuw-moet-uitvinden.html", "source_date": "2025-09-08", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "retail", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 8, "n_chunks_total": 13, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
